OL,3,COxford maternity crisis: Mothers
OL,4,Crecall harrowing ordeals and call for
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FFour mothers who say they had
OL,8,Ftraumatic birth experiences at the
OL,9,FJohn Radcliffe Hospital in Oxford have
OL,10,Ftold ITV Meridian the maternity and
OL,11,Fneonatal departments are responsible
OL,12,Ffor medical negligence, trauma and
OL,13,Fsubstandard care.
OL,15,FThe allegations put towards the
OL,16,Fhospital, part of the Oxford
OL,17,FUniversity's Hospital Trust, begin in
OL,18,F2007 and continue more than 15 years
OL,19,Fon.
