OL,3,COxford maternity crisis: Mothers
OL,4,Crecall harrowing ordeals and call for
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FMore than 500 families who gave birth
OL,8,Fat the John Radcliffe Hospital in
OL,9,FOxford have raised concerns about
OL,10,Fpreventable deaths, traumatic birthing
OL,11,Fexperience, denied caesarians and
OL,12,Fsuffering from PTSD.
OL,14,FA campaign group called Families
OL,15,FFailed by OUH Maternity Services is
OL,16,Fnow calling for judge-led, public,
OL,17,Findependent inquiry.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/15
