OL,3,COxford maternity crisis: Mothers
OL,4,Crecall harrowing ordeals and call for
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FRebeccca Matthews, who herself had a
OL,8,Ftraumatic birth at the hospital, said
OL,9,Fthis would "uncover the extent of the
OL,10,Ffailings that have been happening for
OL,11,Fso many years."
OL,13,FThe campaigner describes a "two tier
OL,14,Fsystem" where if you have a 'normal'
OL,15,Fbirth, your care is good but "if you
OL,16,Fhave a tough birth, or you have
OL,17,Fmedical risk factors, it's almost like
OL,18,Fyou're punished."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/15
