OL,3,COxford maternity crisis: Mothers
OL,4,Crecall harrowing ordeals and call for
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FRachel Hope, from Wantage, said she
OL,8,Fexperienced a traumatic birth with her
OL,9,Fnow 8 year old daughter Savannah.
OL,11,FShe said she was repeatedly denied a
OL,12,Fcaesarian in 2017 despite clear risk
OL,13,Ffactors. Her labour stalled at 4cm but
OL,14,Fstaff continued to administer drugs.
OL,16,FFollowing 2 days in labour - staff
OL,17,Fdecided an emergency c-section was now
OL,18,Fnecessary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/15
