OL,3,COxford maternity crisis: Mothers
OL,4,Crecall harrowing ordeals and call for
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"I overheard a consultant saying
OL,8,F'you've pushed this baby too far' to
OL,9,Fmidwives'", Hope said.
OL,11,F"They could have acted sooner to get
OL,12,Fmy baby out.
OL,14,F"The result of this for my daughter
OL,15,Fwas she ended up with a hole near her
OL,16,Flung, we ended up staying for the best
OL,17,Fpart of 2 weeks."
OL,19,FWhen she realised so many other women
OL,20,Fhad experienced similar experiences at
OL,21,Fthe hospital she was angry.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/15
