OL,4,Crecall harrowing ordeals and call for
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"We really took for granted that you
OL,8,Fgo into hospital, you expect to come
OL,9,Fout safely and you expect to be cared
OL,10,Ffor, and you expect to be listened to.
OL,12,F"I didn't feel that happened at all.
OL,14,F"It has left me with life long scars."
OL,16,FIn October 2024, Kelly McDermott's son
OL,17,FFreddie died three days after birth.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/15
