OL,7,FSe believes she was the victim of a
OL,8,Fnumber of medical failings, including
OL,9,Fdelayed treatment for an infection,
OL,10,Fwhich led to him passing away.
OL,12,FThe hospital said Freddie's death was
OL,13,Fthe result of 'tragic prematurity'.
OL,15,FThe maternity unit was rated "requires
OL,16,Fimprovement" in its last inspection by
OL,17,Fthe government's watchdog, the Care
OL,18,FQuality Commission, in September 2021.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/15
