OL,3,COxford maternity crisis: Mothers
OL,4,Crecall harrowing ordeals and call for
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FThe CQC flagged issues around
OL,8,Fmaintaining patient dignity, and said
OL,9,Fmedicines were not always safely
OL,10,Fstored and managed. The unit did not
OL,11,Fmanage the control of infection
OL,12,Fconsistently it said, and wards were
OL,13,Fnot always kept clean.
OL,15,FThe campaign group is meeting the
OL,16,FChief Nurse of Oxford University
OL,17,FHospitals, Yvonne Christley, in
OL,18,FSeptember to discuss their concerns.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/15
