OL,3,COxford maternity crisis: Mothers
OL,4,Crecall harrowing ordeals and call for
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,FChristley told ITV News Meridian they
OL,8,Fare "committed to deliver safe, high
OL,9,Fquality and outstanding care" and want
OL,10,Fto reassure mothers that their
OL,11,Fservices are safe.
OL,13,FThe Hospital has invested over #3m in
OL,14,Fthe last 2 years increasing staffing
OL,15,Fin the maternity department, enhancing
OL,16,Fits leadership and improving their
OL,17,Ffacilities - including new specific
OL,18,Fbereavement services
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/15
