OL,4,Crecall harrowing ordeals and call for
OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"Our safety and our neonatal and
OL,8,Fmaternity outcomes are really good,"
OL,9,Fsaid Christley. "We do know that as a
OL,10,Fservice we have areas we wish to focus
OL,11,Fon and improve, particularly this is
OL,12,Faround patient experience."
OL,14,FChristley said she had read all the
OL,15,Ftestimonials from the group and they
OL,16,F"make for distressing read" and is
OL,17,F"deeply sorry to all the women and
OL,18,Ffamilies who feel we have let them
OL,19,Fdown, particularly at a time when we
OL,20,Fneeded them."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/15
