OL,7,FIn a separate statement, they said
OL,8,Fwhen they hear an incident of which
OL,9,Fwomen or families feel they are not
OL,10,Fgiven the service they should: "When
OL,11,Fthis happens, we make every effort to
OL,12,Freview individual cases to understand
OL,13,Fwhat went wrong and how we can
OL,14,Fimprove. We are never complacent and
OL,15,Fwelcome all feedback, whether positive
OL,16,For negative, as we learn from both.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/15
