OL,5,Cinquiry
OL,7,F"We also make every effort in such
OL,8,Fcases to keep the woman and family
OL,9,Finformed of what action we have taken
OL,10,Fto improve and what lessons we have
OL,11,Flearnt.
OL,13,F"The Trust has committed to
OL,14,Fmaintaining an ongoing and open
OL,15,Fdialogue with patient groups and
OL,16,Ffamilies, and we acknowledge the
OL,17,Fsignificant role that campaign groups
OL,18,Fplay in expressing concerns and
OL,19,Fadvocating for improvements."
